om Fields'=>'自定义字段','Details'=>'详细信息','Field Status'=>'字段状态','Field Slug'=>'字段 Slug','The slug is used in code to reference this author field. It is all lowercase and contains only letters, numbers, and hyphens.'=>'此 slug 用于代码中引用此作者字段。它全部为小写，仅包含字母、数字和短横线。','Field Type'=>'字段类型','Social Profile?'=>'社交资料？','This feature will add the SameAs property to this link so that search engines realize that the social profile is connected to this author.'=>'此功能将为此链接添加 SameAs 属性，以便搜索引擎意识到社交资料与此作者相关联。','Add a Schema.org property to this field. Examples include alumniOf, worksFor, and birthPlace. %1$sClick here for documentation.%2$s'=>'在此字段中添加 Schema.org 属性。示例包括 alumniOf、worksFor 和 birthPlace。%1$s点击此处查看文档。%2$s','Show in REST API'=>'在 REST API 中显示','Yes'=>'是','Control whether this field is included in REST API responses.'=>'控制此字段是否包含在 REST API 响应中。','Open Link in New Tab'=>'在新标签页中打开链接','This feature will add the target=”_blank” attribute to your link.'=>'此功能将向您的链接添加 target=”_blank” 属性。','Link Rel'=>'链接关系','Requirement'=>'要求','Description'=>'描述','This description appears under the fields and helps users understand their choice.'=>'此描述显示在字段下方，以帮助用户理解他们的选择。','Status'=>'状态','Type'=>'类型','Job Title'=>'职位名称','With PublishPress Authors Pro, you can add new fields for social networks and more.'=>'使用 PublishPress Authors Pro，您可以为社交网络和更多内容添加新字段。','Field Order updated.'=>'字段顺序已更新。','Facebook'=>'Facebook','Please enter the full URL to your Facebook profile.'=>'请输入您 Facebook 个人资料的完整 URL。','X'=>'X','Please enter the full URL to your X profile.'=>'请输入您的 X 个人资料的完整 URL。','Instagram'=>'Instagram','Please enter the full URL to your Instagram page.'=>'请输入您的 Instagram 页面完整 URL。','LinkedIn'=>'LinkedIn','Please enter the full URL to your LinkedIn profile.'=>'请输入您的 LinkedIn 个人资料的完整 URL。','YouTube'=>'YouTube','Please enter the full URL to your YouTube channel.'=>'请输入您的 YouTube 频道的完整 URL。','TikTok'=>'TikTok','Please enter the full URL to your TikTok profile.'=>'请输入您的 TikTok 个人资料的完整 URL。','Author List'=>'作者列表','Add support for author list.'=>'添加对作者列表的支持。','Author Lists'=>'作者列表','Settings updated successfully.'=>'设置已成功更新。','Author List deleted successfully.'=>'作者列表已成功删除。','Author List restored from the Trash.'=>'作者列表已从回收站恢复。','Author List moved to the Trash.'=>'作者列表已移至回收站。','Add New'=>'添加新内容','Search results for &#8220;%s&#8221;'=>'搜索结果为 &#8220;%s&#8221;','Search Author Lists'=>'搜索作者列表','Preview'=>'预览','Users'=>'用户','Options'=>'选项','The original size of the uploaded image'=>'上传图像的原始大小','Large-sized image (1024px by 1024px)'=>'大尺寸图像（1024px x 1024px）','Medium-large image (768px)'=>'中大尺寸图像（768px）','Medium-sized image (300px by 300px)'=>'中尺寸图像（300px x 300px）','Small-sized image (150px by 150px)'=>'小尺寸图像（150px x 150px）','Layout Columns'=>'布局列','Group By'=>'分组依据','Featured Image Size'=>'特色图像大小','Show Authors'=>'显示作者','Select an option to limit the results to selected user roles, author types, specific authors or author Categories.'=>'选择一个选项以限制结果为选定的用户角色、作者类型、特定作者或作者类别。','Roles'=>'角色','Exclude Authors'=>'排除作者','Select an option to exclude selected user roles, author types, specific authors or author Categories from Author list.'=>'选择一个选项以从作者列表中排除选定的用户角色、作者类型、特定作者或作者类别。','Authors Per Page'=>'每页作者数','You can set the number of authors to show per page.'=>'您可以设置每页显示的作者数量。','Show Empty'=>'显示空白','Enable this option to show all authors, including those without any posts. Disable this option to show only authors who are assigned to posts.'=>'启用此选项以显示所有作者，包括没有任何文章的作者。禁用此选项以仅显示分配了文章的作者。','Configure Author List Options'=>'配置作者列表选项','Authors Pro allows you to add extra features to the Authors List. These features include pagination, choose the order of authors, and much more.'=>'Authors Pro 允许您向作者列表添加额外功能。这些功能包括分页、选择作者排序等。','Order By'=>'排序依据','Last Article Date'=>'最后文章日期','You can limit the author list to users with a published post within a specific time. This option accepts date values such as 1 week ago, 1 month ago, 6 months ago, 1 year ago etc.'=>'您可以将作者列表限制为在特定时间内发布文章的用户。此选项接受日期值，例如 1 周前、1 个月前、6 个月前、1 年前等。','Show Search Box'=>'显示搜索框','Add Search Box to Author Lists'=>'将搜索框添加到作者列表','Author Pro allows you to add a search box to the Authors List. You can also show a dropdown menu that allows users to search on specific author fields.'=>'Author Pro 允许您向作者列表添加搜索框。您还可以显示一个下拉菜单，允许用户在特定作者字段上进行搜索。','Search Field Dropdown'=>'搜索字段下拉菜单','You can also show a dropdown menu that allows users to search on specific author fields.'=>'您还可以显示一个下拉菜单，允许用户在特定作者字段上进行搜索。','Author Recent List'=>'作者最近列表','Author Index List'=>'作者索引列表','Edit Author List'=>'编辑作者列表','Add Author List'=>'添加作者列表','Save Changes'=>'保存更改','Dynamic Shortcode'=>'动态短代码','Static Shortcode'=>'静态短代码','Select some options'=>'选择一些选项','Select Users'=>'选择用户','Select Author Category'=>'选择作者类别','This is a quick preview of this Author List. Test on frontend pages to see exactly how it looks with your theme.'=>'这是作者列表的快速预览。在前端页面上测试以查看其在您的主题中的确切外观。','Invalid form'=>'无效表单','AuthorList'=>'作者列表','All %s'=>'所有 %s','Trash %s'=>'垃圾箱 %s','No author list avaliable in the selected view.'=>'所选视图中没有可用的作者列表。','Trash'=>'垃圾箱','Restore'=>'恢复','Delete Permanently'=>'永久删除','Author Pages'=>'作者页面','Add support for author pages.'=>'添加对作者页面的支持。','Author Bio'=>'作者简介','Author Page Title'=>'作者页面标题','Migrate Byline Data'=>'迁移署名数据','Add migration option for Byline'=>'为署名添加迁移选项','Collecting data for the migration...'=>'正在收集迁移数据...','Error: '=>'错误: ','Done! Byline data was copied and you can deactivate the plugin.'=>'完成！署名数据已被复制，您可以停用插件。','Copying authors\' data...'=>'正在复制作者的数据...','Deactivating Byline...'=>'正在停用署名...','Done! Byline is deactivated.'=>'完成！副标题已停用。','Deactivate Byline'=>'停用副标题','Copy Byline Data'=>'复制副标题数据','Migrate Bylines Data'=>'迁移副标题数据','Add migration option for Bylines'=>'为副标题添加迁移选项','Done! Bylines data was copied and you can deactivate the plugin.'=>'完成！副标题数据已复制，您可以停用插件。','Deactivating Bylines...'=>'正在停用副标题...','Done! Bylines is deactivated.'=>'完成！副标题已停用。','Deactivate Bylines'=>'停用副标题','Copy Bylines Data'=>'复制副标题数据','Debug'=>'调试','Add debug information for the plugin'=>'为插件添加调试信息','Authors Debug'=>'作者调试','Default Layouts'=>'默认布局','Authors Index'=>'作者索引','Authors Recent'=>'作者最近','Divi Integration'=>'Divi 集成','Add compatibility with the Divi Theme Builder'=>'与 Divi 主题构建器兼容','Edit Flow Integration'=>'编辑流程集成','Add compatibility with the Edit Flow plugin'=>'与编辑流程插件兼容','Elementor Integration'=>'Elementor 集成','Add compatibility with the Elementor and Elementor Pro page builder'=>'添加与 Elementor 和 Elementor Pro 页面构建器的兼容性','Generatepress Integration'=>'Generatepress 集成','Add compatibility with the Generatepress theme'=>'添加与 Generatepress 主题的兼容性','Genesis Integration'=>'Genesis 集成','Add compatibility with the Genesis framework'=>'添加与 Genesis 框架的兼容性','Authors Settings'=>'作者设置','Features'=>'功能','Feel free to select only the features you need.'=>'请随意选择您需要的功能。','Enabled features'=>'启用的功能','Recommendations for you'=>'为您推荐','Showcase your Authors with PublishPress Blocks'=>'使用 PublishPress Blocks 展示您的作者','PublishPress Blocks is a free plugin with full support for PublishPress Authors.'=>'PublishPress Blocks 是一个免费插件，完全支持 PublishPress Authors。','Install this plugin to showcase content by your Authors.'=>'安装此插件以展示您的作者的内容。','Use the Content Display block to show your posts in many beautiful layouts.'=>'使用内容展示块以多种美观布局显示您的文章。','PublishPress Blocks has over 20 extra Gutenberg blocks including accordions, galleries, tables, and more.'=>'PublishPress Blocks 包含超过 20 个额外的 Gutenberg 块，包括手风琴、图库、表格等。','Click here to install PublishPress Blocks'=>'点击这里安装 PublishPress Blocks','Migrate Molongui Data'=>'迁移 Molongui 数据','Add migration option for Molongui Authorship'=>'为 Molongui 作者身份添加迁移选项','Done! Molongui Authorship data was copied and you can deactivate the plugin.'=>'完成！Molongui 作者身份数据已复制，您可以停用此插件。','Migrating data...'=>'正在迁移数据...','Deactivating Molongui Authorship...'=>'正在停用 Molongui Authorship...','Done! Molongui Authorship is deactivated.'=>'完成！Molongui Authorship 已停用。','Deactivate Molongui Authorship'=>'停用 Molongui Authorship','Copy Molongui Authorship Data'=>'复制 Molongui Authorship 数据','This action will copy the authors from the plugin Molongui Authorship allowing you to migrate to PublishPress Authors without losing any data including post author relation. This action can be run multiple times.'=>'此操作将从插件 Molongui Authorship 复制作者，允许您在不丢失任何数据（包括文章作者关系）的情况下迁移到 PublishPress Authors。此操作可以多次运行。','It looks like you have Molongui Authorship installed.'=>'看起来您已安装 Molongui Authorship。','Please click here to migrate to PublishPress Authors'=>'请点击这里迁移到 PublishPress Authors','Dismiss'=>'关闭','Multiple Authors'=>'多个作者','Pages'=>'页面','Author Profile'=>'作者档案','Settings'=>'设置','Enable PublishPress Authors for these post types:'=>'为这些帖子类型启用 PublishPress Authors：','Post types to display on the author\'s profile page:'=>'在作者档案页面上显示的帖子类型：','Roles available for Author Profiles:'=>'可用于作者档案的角色：','Automatically create author profiles:'=>'自动创建作者档案：','Show username in the search field:'=>'在搜索字段中显示用户名：','Default author for new posts:'=>'新帖子默认作者：','Fallback user for Guest Authors:'=>'访客作者的后备用户：','Remove single author map restriction:'=>'移除单个作者地图限制：','Show above the content:'=>'内容上方显示：','Show below the content:'=>'内容下方显示：','Show Author Box selection:'=>'显示作者框选择：','Disable the "Authors" box when using "Quick Edit":'=>'使用“快速编辑”时禁用“作者”框：','Default Layout:'=>'默认布局：','Title for the author box:'=>'作者框标题：','Color scheme:'=>'配色方案：','Show email link:'=>'显示电子邮件链接：','Show site link:'=>'显示站点链接：','Font Awesome icons:'=>'Font Awesome 图标：','Enable author pages:'=>'启用作者页面：','Author pages posts limit:'=>'作者页面帖子限制：','Author pages layout:'=>'作者页面布局：','Grid layout column:'=>'网格布局列：','Show author bio:'=>'显示作者简介：','Author bio layout:'=>'作者简介布局：','Show author page title:'=>'显示作者页面标题：','Author pages excerpt ellipsis:'=>'作者页面摘要省略号：','Author pages title header:'=>'作者页面标题头部：','Author post title header:'=>'作者帖子标题头：','Show featured image:'=>'显示特色图片：','Link featured image to post:'=>'将特色图片链接到帖子：','Featured image custom width:'=>'特色图片自定义宽度：','Featured image custom height:'=>'特色图片自定义高度：','Show excerpt:'=>'显示摘要：','Show authors:'=>'显示作者：','Show post date:'=>'显示帖子日期：','Show comment counts:'=>'显示评论数量：','Show category:'=>'显示分类：','Show tags:'=>'显示标签：','Show read more link:'=>'显示“阅读更多”链接：','Enable Guest Author With No User Account'=>'启用没有用户账户的访客作者','Enable Guest Author With User Account'=>'启用有用户账户的访客作者','Allow users to opt out of Author Boxes'=>'允许用户选择不显示作者框','Boxed legacy layout Author Box:'=>'盒式传统布局作者框：','Centered legacy layout Author Box:'=>'居中传统布局作者框：','Inline legacy layout Author Box:'=>'内联传统布局作者框：','Inline avatar legacy layout Author Box:'=>'内联头像传统布局作者框：','Simple list legacy layout Author Box:'=>'简单列表传统布局作者框：','Disabled because add_post_type_support(\'%1$s\', \'%2$s\') is included in a loaded file.'=>'已禁用，因为 add_post_type_support(\'%1$s\', \'%2$s\') 已包含在加载的文件中。','This will display the authors box at the top of the content.'=>'这将在内容顶部显示作者框。','This will display the authors box at the end of the content.'=>'这将在内容末尾显示作者框。','Allow users to choose which Author Box is used on each post.'=>'允许用户选择在每个帖子中使用哪个作者框。','Single'=>'单个','Plural'=>'复数','Authors Box'=>'作者框','With this shortcode you can display the author box in any part of the content. '=>'使用此短代码，您可以在内容的任何部分显示作者框。','You can specify layout by using author boxes layout slug. You can see full details of each layout option %1$s in this guide %2$s.'=>'您可以使用作者框布局别名指定布局。您可以在此指南 %2$s 中查看每个布局选项的完整详细信息 %1$s。','You can also decide whether or not to show the main title, using %1$s or %2$s .'=>'您还可以决定是否显示主标题，使用 %1$s 或 %2$s。','You can load the authors for a specific post, even if you are not in that post currently. For example, this shortcode will load the authors for the post with the ID of 32.'=>'您可以为特定文章加载作者，即使您当前不在该文章中。例如，此短代码将加载 ID 为 32 的文章的作者。','You can load the authors for a specific user by providing the user id. For example, this shortcode will load the author with user id of 32'=>'您可以通过提供用户 ID 为特定用户加载作者。例如，此短代码将加载用户 ID 为 32 的作者。','You can load the authors for a specific author by providing the author term id for both guest and user author. For example, this shortcode will load the author with term id of 32'=>'您可以通过提供作者术语 ID 为特定作者加载作者，适用于访客和用户作者。例如，此短代码将加载术语 ID 为 32 的作者。','If you are having problems showing PublishPress Authors on author profile pages, you can use this shortcode below. The argument %s forces the plugin to retrieve the Author from the profile page and not any other posts on the same screen.'=>'如果您在作者个人资料页面上显示 PublishPress Authors 时遇到问题，可以使用下面的短代码。参数 %s 强制插件从个人资料页面检索作者，而不是同一屏幕上的其他文章。','There is one final option to mention. This is mostly useful if you\'re using a theme or page builder to customize the Author profile pages you find at URLs such as /author/username/. You can use the following shortcode on the authors page to display the profile of the current author. You just need to add the parameter %s.'=>'还有一个最终的选项需要提及。这在您使用主题或页面构建器自定义您在 /author/username/ 等 URL 找到的作者档案页面时非常有用。您可以在作者页面上使用以下短代码来显示当前作者的档案。您只需要添加参数 %s。','You can load the authors belonging to a specific author categories by providing the category slug or slugs separated by comma for more than one category.'=>'您可以通过提供类别别名或用逗号分隔的多个类别别名来加载属于特定作者类别的作者。','Authors Data'=>'作者数据','With this shortcode you can display the author names or any profile field in any part of the content.'=>'使用此短代码，您可以在内容的任何部分显示作者名称或任何档案字段。','The authors data shortcode accepts field parameter such as: %1$s %2$s %3$s %4$s %5$s %6$s %7$s. You can see full details and parameters %8$s in this guide %9$s.'=>'作者数据短代码接受字段参数，例如：%1$s %2$s %3$s %4$s %5$s %6$s %7$s。您可以在本指南 %8$s 中查看完整细节和参数 %9$s。','You can also specify the separator to be used for mulitple authors data.'=>'您还可以指定用于多个作者数据的分隔符。','You can retrieve a specific author by providing the author\'s term ID. For example, this shortcode will load the author with the term ID of 102.'=>'您可以通过提供作者的术语 ID 来检索特定作者。例如，此短代码将加载术语 ID 为 102 的作者。','You can also decide to return an array list of authors by using user_objects="true" which will return all the authors object data as an array. You can check full details and sample usage %2$s in this guide%3$s.'=>'您还可以选择通过使用 user_objects="true" 返回作者的数组列表，这将作为数组返回所有作者对象数据。您可以在本指南 %2$s 中查看完整细节和示例用法 %3$s。','You can retrieve authors belonging to a specific Author Category by providing the category slug or slugs. Separate multiple slugs with a comma.'=>'您可以通过提供类别别名来检索属于特定作者类别的作者。用逗号分隔多个别名。','With this shortcode, you can show all the authors together in a single display.'=>'使用此短代码，您可以将所有作者一起显示在一个单一的展示中。','You can specify layout by using author boxes layout slug. You can see full details of each layout option %1$s in this guide %2$s. %3$s %4$s This shortcode also provides two custom layouts: %5$s %6$s.'=>'您可以通过使用作者框布局别名来指定布局。您可以在本指南 %1$s 中查看每个布局选项的完整细节 %2$s。%3$s %4$s 此短代码还提供两个自定义布局：%5$s %6$s。','You can define the number of layout columns by using %1$s to show authors in 2 column.'=>'您可以通过使用 %1$s 定义布局列的数量，以在 2 列中显示作者。','You can choose the number of authors per page using %1$s . %2$s Pagination will be automatically added if required.'=>'您可以使用 %1$s 选择每页的作者数量。%2$s 如果需要，将自动添加分页。','You can limit the result to only authors who are assigned to posts by using %1$s . %2$s Alternatively, use %3$s to show all authors, including those without any posts.'=>'您可以使用 %1$s 将结果限制为仅分配给帖子作者。%2$s 另外，使用 %3$s 显示所有作者，包括那些没有帖子的人。','You can limit the result to only guest authors by using %1$s . %2$s Alternatively, %3$s will show only authors with a WordPress account.'=>'您可以使用 %1$s 将结果限制为仅访客作者。%2$s 另外，%3$s 将仅显示具有 WordPress 账户的作者。','If you are using the authors_recent layout, you can define the number of columns by using %1$s .'=>'如果您使用的是 authors_recent 布局，您可以通过使用 %1$s 定义列的数量。','For authors_index layout, you can group user by profile field by using %1$s .'=>'对于 authors_index 布局，您可以通过使用 %1$s 按档案字段对用户进行分组。','To order the results based on post count, use %1$s . To order the results by name, use %2$s . Alternatively, you can order by profile fields like %3$s, %4$s etc'=>'要根据帖子数量对结果进行排序，请使用 %1$s 。要按名称对结果进行排序，请使用 %2$s 。另外，您可以按档案字段排序，例如 %3$s、%4$s 等等。','To further customize the order of results, use %1$s or %2$s .'=>'要进一步自定义结果的顺序，请使用%1$s或%2$s。','To display a search box for authors, use %1$s .'=>'要显示作者的搜索框，请使用%1$s。','You can also show a dropdown menu that allows users to search on specific author fields. You can add fields to the dropdown using %1$s . This requires the search box to be active.'=>'您还可以显示一个下拉菜单，允许用户在特定作者字段上进行搜索。您可以使用 %1$s 将字段添加到下拉菜单中。这要求搜索框处于活动状态。','You can limit the author list to users with a published post within a specific period using %1$s . This accept english date value like 1 week ago, 1 month ago, 6 months ago, 1 year ago etc.'=>'您可以使用 %1$s 将作者列表限制为在特定期间内发布过帖子用户。这接受英语日期值，例如 1 周前、1 个月前、6 个月前、1 年前等。','Copied!'=>'已复制！','Click To Copy!'=>'点击复制！','Select roles'=>'选择角色','Choose which WordPress user roles can be selected using the "Registered Author With User Account" option for author profiles.'=>'选择可以使用“具有用户账户的注册作者”选项选择的 WordPress 用户角色。','Author profiles can be mapped to WordPress user accounts. This option allows you to automatically create author profiles when users are created in these roles. You can also do this for existing users by clicking the "Create PublishPress Authors Profiles for all users in a role" button in the Maintenance tab.'=>'作者档案可以映射到 WordPress 用户账户。此选项允许您在这些角色中创建用户时自动创建作者档案。您还可以通过单击维护选项卡中的“为角色中的所有用户创建 PublishPress 作者档案”按钮来为现有用户执行此操作。','If the Author is mapped to a WordPress user, this will display the authors\' "Display name" and their "Username". The default is to show only the "Display name". Showing the "Username" is useful if you have several authors with similar names.'=>'如果作者被映射到一个 WordPress 用户，这将显示作者的 "显示名称" 和他们的 "用户名"。默认情况下只显示 "显示名称"。如果您有多个名称相似的作者，显示 "用户名" 是很有用的。','Allow authors to be created without a real user account.'=>'允许在没有真实用户账户的情况下创建作者。','Show a profile checkbox allowing Authors to be excluded from Author Boxes.'=>'显示一个复选框，允许作者从作者框中排除。','Allow authors to be created without a connected user account.'=>'允许在没有连接的用户账户的情况下创建作者。','If enabled, PublishPress Authors will replace the default WordPress author pages.'=>'如果启用，PublishPress Authors 将替换默认的 WordPress 作者页面。','Please note this feature will not work for all themes.'=>'请注意，此功能并不适用于所有主题。','Click here for more details.'=>'点击此处获取更多详细信息。','View sample Author Page'=>'查看示例作者页面','List'=>'列表','Grid'=>'网格','Allow User to Choose'=>'允许用户选择','First Name Last Name'=>'名 姓','Last Name First Name'=>'姓 名','This avatar will be used as default avatar instead of gravatar where no custom avatar is added to profile.'=>'如果没有为个人资料添加自定义头像，则此头像将用作默认头像，而不是 Gravatar。','This will display the author bio.'=>'这将显示作者简介。','Select option'=>'选择选项','This is useful if you use legacy shortcode %s'=>'如果您使用遗留短代码 %s，这将很有用','This will display the featured image.'=>'这将显示特色图片。','This will make the featured image clickable and link to the post.'=>'这将使特色图片可点击并链接到帖子。','This will display author page title.'=>'这将显示作者页面标题。','This will display the excerpt.'=>'这将显示摘录。','This will allows you map a WordPress user to more than one author. Don\'t use this feature unless requested to do so by the PublishPress team. This plugin works better when authors and users are paired one-to-one.'=>'这将允许您将一个 WordPress 用户映射到多个作者。除非 PublishPress 团队要求，否则请不要使用此功能。当作者和用户一对一配对时，此插件效果更好。','This will display the authors.'=>'这将显示作者。','This will display the published date.'=>'这将显示发布时间。','This will display the comment count.'=>'这将显示评论数量。','This will display the categories.'=>'这将显示类别。','This will display the tags.'=>'这将显示标签。','This will display the read more link.'=>'这将显示“阅读更多”链接。','This setting may be disabled for users who can not edit others posts.'=>'此设置可能会对无法编辑他人帖子用户禁用。','Search for a fallback author'=>'搜索备用作者','If you only have Guest Authors selected for a post, this user may be used as a fallback. WordPress sometimes requires a WordPress user to be assigned to each post. This user will not be visible on the front of your site.'=>'如果您仅为帖子选择了访客作者，则此用户可以用作后备。WordPress 有时要求每个帖子分配一个 WordPress 用户。此用户将在您网站的前端不可见。','This will display the authors email in the author box.'=>'这将显示作者邮箱在作者框中。','This will display the authors site in the author box.'=>'这将显示作者网站在作者框中。','This will load Font Awesome icons for use in Author Boxes.'=>'这将加载Font Awesome图标以供作者框使用。','This will remove the Authors Box in "Quick Edit".'=>'这将删除“快速编辑”中的作者框。','Create PublishPress Authors Profiles for all post authors'=>'为所有帖子作者创建PublishPress作者档案','If a WordPress user is the author of a post, but does not have a PublishPress Authors profile, this will automatically create a profile for them.'=>'如果一个 WordPress 用户是帖子的作者，但没有 PublishPress Authors 个人资料，这将自动为他们创建一个个人资料。','Click here for documentation'=>'点击此处查看文档','Create missing PublishPress Authors profiles'=>'创建缺失的PublishPress作者档案','Create PublishPress Authors Profiles for all users in a role'=>'为角色中的所有用户创建 PublishPress 作者档案','This will find all the users in a role and create author profiles for them. You can choose the roles using the "Automatically create author profiles" setting.'=>'这将找到角色中的所有用户并为他们创建作者个人资料。您可以使用 "自动创建作者个人资料" 设置选择角色。','Create PublishPress Authors profiles'=>'创建 PublishPress 作者档案','Synchronize PublishPress Authors Fields and user profile fields'=>'同步 PublishPress 作者字段和用户档案字段','This will update all the author profiles in PublishPress Authors to match the default WordPress fields for each user.'=>'这将更新 PublishPress Authors 中的所有作者个人资料，以匹配每个用户的默认 WordPress 字段。','Synchronize the author and user URLs'=>'同步作者和用户的 URL','This will update all the Author URLs in PublishPress Authors to match the default WordPress URLs for each user.'=>'这将更新 PublishPress Authors 中的所有作者 URL，以匹配每个用户的默认 WordPress URL。','Create Author Categories'=>'创建作者分类','This will create author categories table if missing and add default categories.'=>'如果缺失，这将创建作者类别表并添加默认类别。','Copy Co-Authors Plus Data'=>'复制 Co-Authors Plus 数据','This action will copy the authors from the plugin Co-Authors Plus allowing you to migrate to PublishPress Authors without losing any data. This action can be run multiple times.'=>'此操作将从插件 Co-Authors Plus 复制作者，允许您在不丢失任何数据的情况下迁移到 PublishPress Authors。此操作可以多次运行。','Delete Connections Between Author Profiles and Users'=>'删除作者档案与用户之间的连接','This action can reset the PublishPress Authors data before using other maintenance options. It will delete all author profiles that are mapped to a WordPress user account. This will not delete the WordPress user accounts, but any links between the posts and author profiles will be lost.'=>'此操作可以在使用其他维护选项之前重置 PublishPress Authors 数据。它将删除所有与 WordPress 用户帐户映射的作者个人资料。这不会删除 WordPress 用户帐户，但帖子和作者个人资料之间的任何链接将丢失。','Delete all authors mapped to users'=>'删除所有映射到用户的作者','Delete Guest Authors'=>'删除访客作者','This action can reset the PublishPress Authors data before using other maintenance options. Guest authors are author profiles that are not mapped to a WordPress user account. This action will delete all guest authors.'=>'此操作可以在使用其他维护选项之前重置 PublishPress Authors 数据。访客作者是未映射到 WordPress 用户帐户的作者个人资料。此操作将删除所有访客作者。','Delete all guest authors'=>'删除所有访客作者','Please be careful clicking these buttons. Before clicking, we recommend taking a site backup in case anything goes wrong.'=>'请小心点击这些按钮。在点击之前，我们建议进行网站备份，以防出现任何问题。','Author Profiles'=>'作者档案','Integration'=>'集成','Maintenance'=>'维护','Advanced'=>'高级','Invalid nonce'=>'无效的随机数','Access denied'=>'访问被拒绝','Error. Author terms could not be reseted.'=>'错误。无法重置作者条款。','Maintenance completed successfully.'=>'维护成功完成。','Collecting data...'=>'正在收集数据...','Finishing the process...'=>'正在完成过程...','Done! %d posts were updated.'=>'完成！%d 篇文章已更新。','Updating author field on posts...'=>'正在更新文章中的作者字段...','Updated %d of %d posts...'=>'更新了 %d 篇中的 %d 篇文章...','Sync author and user URLs'=>'同步作者和用户网址','Done! %d authors were updated.'=>'完成！%d 位作者已更新。','Updating authors slug...'=>'正在更新作者别名...','Updated %d of %d authors...'=>'更新了 %d 位作者中的 %d 位...','Creating missed post authors....'=>'正在创建缺失的文章作者....','Copy Co-Authors Plus data'=>'复制 Co-Authors Plus 数据','Deactivating Co-uthors Plus...'=>'正在停用 Co-Authors Plus...','Done! Co-Authors Plus is deactivated.'=>'完成！Co-Authors Plus 已停用。','Deactivate Co-Authors Plus'=>'停用 Co-Authors Plus','Done! Co-Authors Plus data was copied.'=>'完成！Co-Authors Plus 数据已复制。','It looks like you have Co-Authors Plus installed.'=>'看起来您已经安装了 Co-Authors Plus。','Please click here and read this guide!'=>'请点击这里阅读此指南！','PublishPress Authors needs a database update for Permissions integration.'=>'PublishPress Authors 需要数据库更新以集成权限。','Click to run the update now'=>'点击立即运行更新','Guest Author cannot login on the site.'=>'访客作者无法登录网站。','Polylang Integration'=>'Polylang 集成','Enable Polylang Author Translation:'=>'启用 Polylang 作者翻译：','Enable translation of author profiles in Polylang.'=>'启用 Polylang 中作者资料的翻译。','Rank Math Seo Integration'=>'Rank Math Seo 集成','Add compatibility with the Rank Math Seo plugin'=>'添加与 Rank Math Seo 插件的兼容性','Rest API'=>'Rest API','Rest API support'=>'Rest API 支持','Guest authors without user accounts is not enabled.'=>'未启用没有用户账户的访客作者。','Guest author with user accounts is not enabled.'=>'未启用带有用户账户的访客作者。','An author with this slug already exists.'=>'具有此别名的作者已经存在。','This WordPress user is already mapped to another author.'=>'此 WordPress 用户已经映射到另一位作者。','Author was created but could not be retrieved.'=>'作者已创建但无法检索。','Author not found.'=>'未找到作者。','You cannot edit author mapped to administrator account.'=>'您无法编辑映射到管理员账户的作者。','You do not have permission to edit this author.'=>'您没有权限编辑此作者。','Reviews'=>'评论','The SEO Framework Integration'=>'SEO框架集成','Add compatibility with The SEO Framework plugin.'=>'添加与SEO框架插件的兼容性。','PublishPress Authors Settings'=>'PublishPress 作者设置','There are no PublishPress modules registered'=>'没有注册的 PublishPress 模块','Ultimate_Post Integration'=>'Ultimate_Post 集成','Add compatibility with the Ultimate Post plugin'=>'添加与 Ultimate Post 插件的兼容性','By'=>'由','Ultimate Member Integration'=>'Ultimate Member 集成','Add compatibility with the Ultimate Member plugin'=>'添加与 Ultimate Member 插件的兼容性','WPEngine Integration'=>'WPEngine 集成','Add compatibility with the WPEngine object cache.'=>'添加与 WPEngine 对象缓存的兼容性。','Yoast SEO Integration'=>'Yoast SEO 集成','Add compatibility with the Yoast SEO plugin'=>'添加与 Yoast SEO 插件的兼容性','Comment counts'=>'评论数量','Prev'=>'上一页','Next'=>'下一页','Post not found for the author'=>'未找到该作者的帖子','Published date'=>'发布日期','If you like %1$s please leave us a %2$s rating. Thank you!'=>'如果您喜欢 %1$s，请给我们留下一个 %2$s 评级。谢谢！','About'=>'关于','Documentation'=>'文档','Contact'=>'联系','taxonomy general nameAuthors'=>'作者','taxonomy singular nameAuthor'=>'作者','Author Box post type name%2$s'=>'%2$s','singular author box post type name%1$s'=>'%1$s','custom layout post type menu name%2$s'=>'%2$s','Custom Field post type name%2$s'=>'%2$s','singular custom field post type name%1$s'=>'%1$s','custom field post type menu name%2$s'=>'%2$s']];